      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LADY BREANNA (3) missed the frame last time but before three back recorded the quickest win (34.63) on the program at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and expected to go close. ABSOLUTE RUPEE (6) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 6th and beaten 13 lengths at this track (31.04). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Better than last start and can bounce back. REV IAN (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Blackpool Winter (30.55) in a Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Can feature again. RATTLER (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
